0e11220de91bd677599327","url_token":"excalibur-65-73","name":"Amendment I","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-6e64891a2c3ccdfff4dbbec006fc95be_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-6e64891a2c3ccdfff4dbbec006fc95be_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/96af55b0660e11220de91bd677599327","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560805709","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545889521,"updated_time":1545889652,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e还高中生证明哥德巴赫猜想，你也太瞧不起哥德巴赫猜想了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cblockquote\u003e哥德巴赫猜想是中国民间科学爱好者热衷研究的数学问题之一。在徐迟的报告文学影响下，不少民间科学爱好者对哥德巴赫猜想产生兴趣，许多人自称在此问题上取得了进展，甚至自称证明了哥德巴赫猜想。中国科学院每年都收到“几麻袋”的讨论或声称证明了哥德巴赫猜想的来信来稿。不少报章也刊登过哥德巴赫猜想被民间科学爱好者证明的消息。许多数学家都认为，缺乏专业的学科知识和系统的训练的人，是无法在哥德巴赫猜想上做出进展的，甚至不可能理解此方面的研究。数学家建议，相关爱好者在研究哥德巴赫猜想之前至少应当“系统掌握相应的数学知识，以免走不必要的弯路”。中国科学院数学与系统科学研究院研究员陆柱家称“业余研究者是无法证明这个猜想（哥德巴赫猜想）的，除非世界一流的数学家，否则无法求证”、“哥德巴赫猜想是一个艰深的数论难题，证明它所需要的数学能力和突出的思维能力，都并非普通数学爱好者所能企及”。中国科学院已声明不会审理来自科学共同体之外的任何自称证明了哥德巴赫猜想的文章。\u003c/blockquote\u003e\u003cp\u003e来源：\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%25E5%2593%25A5%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%25B5%25AB%25E7%258C%259C%25E6%2583%25B3\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003ehttps://\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"visible\"\u003ezh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003eE5%93%A5%E5%BE%B7%E5%B7%B4%E8%B5%AB%E7%8C%9C%E6%83%B3\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"ellipsis\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560802631,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0bfafb0c2ad0e1600a257809c1c91c71","url_token":"yan-qian-73-94","name":"燕茜","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0bfafb0c2ad0e1600a257809c1c91c71","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560802631","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545889259,"updated_time":1545890033,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e都证明哥德巴赫猜想了,还想着上大学?真是手高眼低\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560781825,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560781825","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545887380,"updated_time":1545887380,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e多个世界一流学校愿意给你发博士学位\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e多个世界一流学校愿意聘你当终身教授\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e菲尔兹奖提前钦定\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而你\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e却想保送清华北大？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e有点追求行不行啊？！\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560747035,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"35a70fdb0c67a5c6ca078c6a70c6d0ff","url_token":"xiao-fei-pai","name":"小飞派","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/35a70fdb0c67a5c6ca078c6a70c6d0ff","user_type":"people","headline":"有时撕逼，经常黑人，总是吐槽。","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560747035","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545884211,"updated_time":1545884211,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e讲道理，哥德巴赫猜想一般不会被高中生证明，我也不会。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我只想说一下自己的想法，希望题主脚踏实地\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其实当年我有些中二，（羞耻）也是希望自己就用现有的知识和想法来完成一道世界性难题，我也希望自己能够一飞冲天，成为什么什么厉害的人物。（其实现在也有些。。。）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是，这是不可能的，现在的科学知识已经不是一个区区高中生能够掌握的了，现在其实每天都会有新的发现，而且这些发现是很难以理解的，一个专注于小领域的博士生都觉得很吃力，何况一个高中生？微积分，概率论这tm都是一百年前的东西一个高中生都不清楚，怎么能解决一个重大的问题呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其实这是眼界的问题，我在高中的时候，我就知道那些历史书上的内容，什么饶毅什么施一公潘建伟我都不知道，自己只知道的东西就在自己的课桌上，现在到了大学才明白我们的世界不止教科书，论文那么多，我们的世界有很多未知的东西，而且很多厉害的人正在探究他们。（而且这些厉害的人的月工资都比较少。。。）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我希望题主能够进入一个好的大学，不断学习，如果你真的有解决的哥德巴赫问题的勇气和毅力，那现在对于你而言就是进入好的大学，扩宽眼界，看看世界，再看看自己，再来看看自己能够做什么？不能够做什么？我希望题主不是只是在知乎上提出一个这样的问题，我希望题主用自己的行为来证明自己。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560744441,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想